title: Index of Composite Wages for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1820-1909 (2)--Original Data, 1910-1920 (3)--Original Data, 1919-1946 (4)--Original Data, 1938-1949. This Index Is Based On Weekly Earnings. Source: Federal Reserve Board Files, Also Published In Monthly Reviews Of The New York Federal Reserve Bank.

This NBER data series m08061b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
